snippet.title: ブルーアーカイブ Blue Archive OST 7. Unwelcome School
snippet.description:
Composer: Mitsukiyo (Twitter: https://twitter.com/mitsukiyo_5)

Released as Track 1, Disc 1 of OST album Vol. 4

Blue Archive Official Website (JP): https://bluearchive.jp/
Blue Archive Official Website (Global): https://bluearchive.nexon.com/

Stream / Download the albums here -
Vol 1: https://nex-tone.link/A00094941
Vol 2: https://nex-tone.link/A00102108
Vol 3: https://nex-tone.link/A00111577
Vol 4: https://nex-tone.link/A00120144

Blue Archive is an RPG mobile title developed by NAT Games and published by Yostar in Japan and by Nexon globally. The player will be a teacher that leads their students into various incidents around the city.

This video is solely intended for promoting and education purposes and have no means of monetization. This channel is not affiliated with NAT Games, Yostar or Nexon in any ways.
